'''帕特里克·詹姆斯·科尔曼·“帕迪”·麦克奈尔'''（{{lang-en|Patrick James Coleman "Paddy" McNair}}，{{bd|1995年|4月27日|catidx=McNair, Paddy}}）是一名[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[足球员|足球员]]，司职[[后卫_(足球)|后卫]]，效力于[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球队[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]，並代表[[北愛爾蘭國家足球隊|北愛爾蘭國家足球隊]]參加國際比賽。

==职业生涯==
麦克奈尔在12岁时被[[曼彻斯特联足球俱乐部|曼联]]驻北爱尔兰球探托尼库尔特发现，从此他便开始在学校放假时前往曼联进行训练<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/manchester-united/shock-manchester-united-callup-for-ni-starlet-paddy-mcnair-30616319.html |title=Shock Manchester United call-up for NI starlet Paddy McNair |date=27 September 2014 |accessdate=27 September 2014 |work=Belfast Telegraph |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402114539/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/manchester-united/shock-manchester-united-callup-for-ni-starlet-paddy-mcnair-30616319.html }}</ref>。2011年他终于与曼联签约，他在巴里克莱小马队踢中场的表现给曼联的球探们留下了深刻的印象，但是曼联青年队教练{{le|保罗·麦坚尼斯(足球)|Paul McGuinness (footballer)|麦坚尼斯}}后来把他改造成了一个后卫<ref>{{cite news |last=Lynch |first=David |url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/who-man-united-debutant-patrick-7843388 |title=Who is Man United debutant Patrick McNair? |date=27 September 2014 |accessdate=27 September 2014 |work=Manchester Evening News |archive-date=2017-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117122940/http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/who-man-united-debutant-patrick-7843388 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。把他从中场改造为后卫时，麦吉尼斯把麦克奈尔比作[[迈克尔·卡里克|卡里克]]<ref>{{cite news |last=Marshall |first=Adam |url=http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2013/Jun/paul-mcguinness-expects-grimshaw-and-mcnair-to-progress.aspx |title=McGuinness praise for Grimshaw and McNair |date=30 June 2013 |accessdate=27 September 2014 |work=Manchester United F.C. Official Website |archive-date=2017-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117122711/http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Football-News/2013/Jun/paul-mcguinness-expects-grimshaw-and-mcnair-to-progress.aspx }}</ref>。

在2014年9月27日曼联于主场[[老特拉福德球场|老特拉福德球场]]2-1战胜[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联]]的比赛中，麦克奈尔第一次代表曼联在[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英超]]出场<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29394502 |title=NI teenager Paddy McNair handed Man Utd debut against West Ham |date=27 September 2014 |accessdate=27 September 2014 |work=BBC |archive-date=2015-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709015045/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/29394502 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。得益于队中后防线的伤病危机，他得到了首发的机会<ref>{{cite news |last=Jackson |first=Jamie |url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/25/louis-van-gaal-manchester-united-paddy-mcnair-defensive-crisis |title=Manchester United may call on Paddy McNair due to defensive crisis |date=25 September 2014 |accessdate=27 September 2014 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206103713/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/25/louis-van-gaal-manchester-united-paddy-mcnair-defensive-crisis }}</ref>。麦克奈尔在比赛中坚实的防守得到了主教练[[路易斯·范加尔|范加尔]]和球迷们的大加赞扬，在曼联被罚下一人后他还上演了一次至关重要的头球解围<ref>{{cite news |last=Marshall |first=Adam |url=http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Features/2014/Sep/paddy-mcnair-debut-performance-praised.aspx |title=McNair earns his first-team stripes |date=27 September 2014 |accessdate=28 September 2014 |work=Manchester United F.C. Official Website |archive-date=2017-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117122554/http://www.manutd.com/en/News-And-Features/Features/2014/Sep/paddy-mcnair-debut-performance-praised.aspx }}</ref>。

